        "title_e": "日本語の教育が必要な子どものために「支援員」を増やす",
        "date": "2019-07-06",
        "urlnormal": "https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20190706/k10011984121000.html",
        "urleasy": "https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/easy/k10011984121000/k10011984121000.html"
